  <brief_title>Evaluation of Metabolic Activity of Liver Metastases by FDG-PET Scanning</brief_title>
  <official_title>Exploratory Study on FDG-PET Scanning in Evaluating the Metabolic Activity of Liver Metastases Before and After Resection of the Primary Tumor in Patients With a Colorectal Malignancy</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
